javadoc: MergeUtilities provides generic static methods for use by the multi-user program merge managers.

methods.name: adjustSets
methods.comment:
Adds addresses to autoChanges where there are changes in the myDiffs set,
 but none in the latestDiffs set.
 Adds addresses to conflictChanges where there are changes in the myDiffs 
 set and also some changes in the latestDiffs set.

params.name: latestDiffs
params.comment: the address set of the changes in LATEST.

params.name: myDiffs
params.comment: the address set of the changes in MY.

params.name: autoChanges
params.comment: address set for the myDiffs non-conflicting changes.

params.name: conflictChanges
params.comment: address set for the myDiffs conflicting changes
